                            <comment id="13003345" author="srowen" created="Mon, 7 Mar 2011 13:16:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;For tidiness, I think we should consider this a subset of &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MAHOUT-294&quot; title=&quot;Uniform API behavior for Jobs&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;MAHOUT-294&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;MAHOUT-294&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;. The goal is to standardize interaction with Hadoop, really. Stepping towards that goal necessarily means moving off of Hadoop 0.19.x APIs.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
